[
  {
    "dialogue_id": "2ad73a35-7bdc-41d5-8618-657bd924c266",
    "goal": "Book a room at Finches for tonight with a budget price range",
    "domain": "hotel",
    "context": "I'm traveling to the area for a conference and I need a comfortable place to stay for the night. I've heard good things about Finches and I'd like to book a room there. It's important that it's within my budget, as I'm trying to keep expenses low for the trip.",
    "user_persona": "General user (friendly and concise)",
    "turns": [
      {
        "role": "User",
        "text": "Hi, I'm looking for a place to stay tonight and I'm interested in Finches. Can you help me book a room there at a reasonable price?",
        "timestamp": "2026-02-22T18:18:09.103872"
      },
      {
        "role": "SupportBot",
        "text": "I'd be happy to help you book a room at Finches for tonight. Before I check availability, can you tell me a bit more about what you're looking for in terms of budget - are you thinking of something under $100, or is there a bit more flexibility in your price range? This will help me narrow down some options for you at Finches.",
        "timestamp": "2026-02-22T18:18:09.545577"
      },
      {
        "role": "User",
        "text": "I'm aiming for a budget-friendly option, so something under $100 would be ideal, could you check the availability of rooms at Finches within that price range for tonight?",
        "timestamp": "2026-02-22T18:18:09.855046"
      },
      {
        "role": "SupportBot",
        "text": "I've checked the availability of rooms at Finches for tonight, and I found a few options that fit your budget of under $100. They have a single room available for $80, which includes free Wi-Fi and a continental breakfast, and a double room for $90, which also comes with a flat-screen TV and a desk area. Would you like me to proceed with booking one of these rooms for you, or would you like to compare more options?",
        "timestamp": "2026-02-22T18:18:10.258557"
      },
      {
        "role": "User",
        "text": "I'd like to proceed with booking the single room for $80, could you please confirm the booking and provide me with a reference number or confirmation details for my stay at Finches tonight?",
        "timestamp": "2026-02-22T18:18:10.577363"
      },
      {
        "role": "SupportBot",
        "text": "I've confirmed your booking for the single room at Finches for tonight at $80, and your confirmation number is FIN-1234. This room includes free Wi-Fi and a continental breakfast, and you can check-in anytime after 3 pm today. Your room will be ready for you when you arrive, and if you need any further assistance, please don't hesitate to ask.",
        "timestamp": "2026-02-22T18:18:11.006121"
      },
      {
        "role": "User",
        "text": "I've taken note of the confirmation number FIN-1234 and the check-in time after 3 pm, so I'm all set for my stay at Finches tonight; could you just let me know what I should expect in terms of parking options when I arrive?",
        "timestamp": "2026-02-22T18:18:11.423144"
      },
      {
        "role": "SupportBot",
        "text": "For parking options at Finches, you can expect to find a small on-site car park that's available on a first-come, first-served basis, and there are also several public parking lots within a short walking distance from the hotel, including one just across the street with a flat rate of $10 per night. If you'd like, I can provide you with more information on the nearby parking options or offer directions to the on-site car park. Your confirmation number FIN-1234 is",
        "timestamp": "2026-02-22T18:18:12.016932"
      },
      {
        "role": "User",
        "text": "Thank you, that's perfect!",
        "timestamp": "2026-02-22T18:18:12.016947"
      }
    ],
